text: Ba Mamadou dit Mbaré (1946 – 10 January 2013) was a Mauritanian politician. He was President of the Senate of Mauritania from 2006 until his death. In 2009, he was acting President of Mauritania. ==References== Category:1946 births Category:2013 deaths Category:Presidents of Mauritania
title: Ba Mamadou Mbaré
